 not only endorses a return to land rent but does so from a position very
 similar to that of this paper).
 What accounts for this recent interest in land rent? The cited sources
 all give their own reasons for advocating a return to land rent, but in
 light of the most cataclysmic economic event of our time, the Crisis of
 the early 21st Century, one might hope this would be a prime motive 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
before "cf."
key "taylor2012islandlife"
literal "true"

\end_inset

.
 But surprisingly, it is not.
 Leaving aside 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
