literal "true"

\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citeyearpar
key "park2011spatial,park2014landrent"
literal "true"

\end_inset

 explicitly connect resurrecting the study of land rent to the crisis.
 In fact, the term 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

crisis
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 does not even appear in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citeauthor
